      <title>中国粮食需求下降对世界市场构成威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/china-s-waning-appetite-for-grain-spells-danger-for-world-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国对海外小麦和玉米的需求正在迅速减少，这可能会给已经习惯于全球最大农产品进口国强劲需求的世界粮食市场带来压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/china-s-waning-appetite-for-grain-spells-danger-for-world-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 02:55:30 GMT</pubDate>
